[5.922712, "o", "\r\n\u001b[?2004l\r"]
[6.062016, "o", "\r\n🦅 Dativo Talon — Governed Session Demo (#107 Act II)\r\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\nOne real agent session, two real providers, one session budget.\r\n\r\n  Proves: prompt-cache economics · cross-provider session budget\r\n          PII stop · tool governance · signed evidence for all of it\r\n\r\n  Gateway:           http://localhost:8080\r\n  Session:           sess-governed-1783414113\r\n  Planner:           claude-sonnet-5 (Anthropic, real API)\r\n  Executor:          gpt-4o (OpenAI, real API)\r\n  Mode:              enforce (violations blocked before the provider)\r\n\r\n  ⚠ This run makes real API calls (cheap models, session-capped ≈ $0.05).\r\n\r\n"]
[6.077872, "o", "\r\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n[1/7] Planner call — Anthropic prompt-cache WRITE\r\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\n"]
[6.078438, "o", "  The planner sends a ~2.3k-token governed instruction prefix with\r\n  cache_control: ephemeral. Anthropic writes it to the prompt cache;\r\n  Talon records cache_creation_input_tokens as cache_write in evidence."]
[6.078561, "o", "\r\n\r\n"]
[14.06169, "o", "  Request:           planner (cache write)\r\n  HTTP status:       200\r\n"]
[14.072676, "o", "  Response:          # Three Executor Steps: EU AI Act Evidence Duties for Mid-Market SaaS  **Step 1 — Classify & Scope** Determi…\r\n\r\n"]
[14.561792, "o", "    Allowed:       true\r\n    Cost:          $0.013403\r\n    Tokens:        in=39 out=300 cache_read=0 cache_write=2343\r\n    Pricing Basis: table\r\n      [1] POLICY_ALLOWED | allow | Request allowed by policy.\r\n"]
[14.562518, "o", "\r\n  ✓ Planner forwarded — cache write recorded in signed evidence\r\n    → audit show shows cache_write > 0 and its exact cost basis\r\n\r\n"]
[14.579053, "o", "\r\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n[2/7] Planner refinement — Anthropic prompt-cache READ\r\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\n  The second planner call reuses the identical prefix within the cache TTL:\r\n  Anthropic bills those tokens at the cache-read rate (~0.1× input).\r\n  Naïve input×rate math is already wrong from this call onward.\r\n\r\n"]
[18.428899, "o", "  Request:           planner (cache read)\r\n  HTTP status:       200\r\n"]
[18.434984, "o", "  Response:          I don't have a \"step three\" or \"step two\" from prior context in this session — no plan has been shared yet. …\r\n\r\n"]
[18.961754, "o", "    Allowed:       true\r\n    Cost:          $0.001858\r\n    Tokens:        in=25 out=72 cache_read=2343 cache_write=0\r\n    Pricing Basis: table\r\n      [1] POLICY_ALLOWED | allow | Request allowed by policy.\r\n\r\n"]
[18.962656, "o", "  ✓ Cache read recorded — cache_read tokens priced at the read rate\r\n    → Same session, same signed trail, cross-provider spend accumulating\r\n"]
[18.962799, "o", "\r\n"]
[18.977693, "o", "\r\n"]
[18.978498, "o", "─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n[3/7] Executor calls — OpenAI cached prompt + tool governance\r\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────"]
[18.978804, "o", "\r\n\r\n  Executors share the same long prefix, so OpenAI's automatic prompt cache"]
[18.979784, "o", "\r\n  reports cached_tokens on repeat calls. Executor 2 also requests tools —\r\n  including admin_purge_records, which policy forbids (admin_*).\r\n  Talon strips it from the request body before the model can see it.\r\n\r\n"]
[21.974354, "o", "  Request:           executor 1\r\n  HTTP status:       200\r\n"]
[21.982201, "o", "  Response:          GDPR Article 30 mandates that organizations maintain records of processing activities, applicable to AI system…\r\n"]
[21.982448, "o", "\r\n"]
[23.133741, "o", "  Request:           executor 2 (admin_* tool stripped)\r\n"]
[23.134859, "o", "  HTTP status:       200\r\n"]
[23.142512, "o", "\r\n"]
[23.40172, "o", "  Tool governance (talon audit show gw_257a0fa5-596)\r\n"]
[23.662014, "o", "    Tool Governance (gateway)"]
[23.662814, "o", "\r\n"]
[23.663666, "o", "      Requested:  admin_purge_records, search_kb\r\n      Filtered:   admin_purge_records\r\n      Forwarded:  search_kb\r\n"]
[23.663971, "o", "\r\n  ✓ Executors ran governed — forbidden tool never reached the model\r\n    → evidence.ToolGovernance: requested vs filtered vs forwarded\r\n    → cached_tokens appear as cache_read in evidence on repeat calls\r\n\r\n"]
[23.678328, "o", "\r\n"]
[23.678698, "o", "─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n[4/7] PII probe — IBAN stopped before any provider call\r\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\n  Mid-session, a request carries a real-looking German IBAN.\r\n  default_pii_action: block — the request is denied pre-forward;\r\n  no token of it left your boundary, and the deny is signed evidence.\r\n\r\n"]
[23.734607, "o", "  Request:           pii probe (expected deny)"]
[23.73522, "o", "\r\n  HTTP status:       400\r\n"]
[23.743319, "o", "  Response:          Request contains PII that is not allowed …"]
[23.743649, "o", "\r\n\r\n"]
[24.247627, "o", "    Allowed:       false\r\n      Reason:      PII block\r\n    Cost:          $0.000000\r\n    Tokens:        in=0 out=0\r\n      [1] POLICY_DENIED_PII_INPUT | deny | Request blocked because input PII was detected.\r\n"]
[24.247918, "o", "\r\n  ✗ HTTP 400 — POLICY_DENIED_PII_INPUT, zero upstream cost\r\n    → The denial itself is an HMAC-signed evidence record in this session\r\n\r\n"]
[24.265561, "o", "\r\n"]
[24.266757, "o", "─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n[5/7] Session budget gate — loop until the next request is refused\r\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\n  Caller cap: max_session_cost 0.04 (pricing-table currency). Talon sums"]
[24.266888, "o", "\r\n"]
[24.267132, "o", "  REAL spend across Anthropic + OpenAI in this session; each new request"]
[24.267792, "o", "\r\n  is checked as spend + estimate BEFORE forwarding (#198).\r\n  The executor keeps working until the gate closes.\r\n"]
[24.268485, "o", "\r\n"]
[26.505647, "o", "  Request:           executor loop 1\r\n  HTTP status:       200\r\n"]
[26.514292, "o", "  Response:          AI cost accountability involves tracking and managing expenses associated with AI development, deployment, and…"]
[26.515206, "o", "\r\n\r\n"]
[26.783706, "o", "  session spend (Talon evidence): 0.02623965 / cap 0.04\r\n"]
[28.214527, "o", "  Request:           executor loop 2"]
[28.214923, "o", "\r\n  HTTP status:       200\r\n"]
[28.223603, "o", "  Response:          AI cost accountability involves tracking and managing the expenses associated with developing, deploying, and …"]
[28.224267, "o", "\r\n\r\n"]
[28.460626, "o", "  session spend (Talon evidence): 0.02844315 / cap 0.04\r\n"]
[29.951761, "o", "  Request:           executor loop 3\r\n  HTTP status:       200\r\n"]
[29.959508, "o", "  Response:          AI cost accountability involves tracking and managing the expenses associated with deploying and operating AI …\r\n\r\n"]
[30.227309, "o", "  session spend (Talon evidence): 0.03060665 / cap 0.04\r\n"]
[31.944305, "o", "  Request:           executor loop 4\r\n  HTTP status:       200\r\n"]
[31.952937, "o", "  Response:          AI cost accountability in Europe involves tracking and justifying the expenses associated with AI development …\r\n\r\n"]
[32.245431, "o", "  session spend (Talon evidence): 0.03301015 / cap 0.04"]
[32.246802, "o", "\r\n"]
[33.881524, "o", "  Request:           executor loop 5\r\n  HTTP status:       200\r\n"]
[33.890898, "o", "  Response:          AI cost accountability involves tracking and managing AI-related expenditures to ensure transparency and budge…\r\n"]
[33.891327, "o", "\r\n"]
[34.282633, "o", "  session spend (Talon evidence): 0.03533365 / cap 0.04"]
[34.284281, "o", "\r\n"]
[34.357484, "o", "  Request:           executor loop 6\r\n  HTTP status:       403\r\n"]
[34.378283, "o", "  Response:          session spend 0.0353 + estimate 0.0063 exceeds limit 0.04 …\r\n\r\n"]
[35.040345, "o", "    Allowed:       false\r\n      Reason:      session_budget_exceeded: session spend 0.0353 + estimate 0.0063 exceeds limit 0.04\r\n    Cost:          $0.000000\r\n    Tokens:        in=0 out=0\r\n      [1] POLICY_DENIED_COST | deny | Request blocked by cost policy limits.\r\n"]
[35.040903, "o", "\r\n  ✗ HTTP 403 — denied pre-forward, nothing was spent on this request"]
[35.041359, "o", "\r\n    → Reason: session spend 0.0353 + estimate 0.0063 exceeds limit 0.04\r\n    → Evidence carries SessionBudget{limit, spent, estimate} for auditors\r\n\r\n"]
[35.058369, "o", "\r\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────"]
[35.059497, "o", "\r\n[6/7] Money story — misleading naïve total vs Talon's corrected total\r\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\n  Naïve accounting prices every input-side token at the full input rate.\r\n  Talon's evidence prices cache writes at 1.25× and cache reads at ~0.1×,\r\n  exactly as the providers bill. Same session, two very different numbers.\r\n\r\n"]
[35.411379, "o", "  Token classes across the session (from signed evidence):\r\n  cache writes:      2343 tokens (billed 1.25× input rate)"]
[35.4122, "o", "\r\n  cache reads:       7463 tokens (billed ~0.1× input rate)\r\n\r\n"]
[35.416809, "o", "  Naïve total  (all input-side tokens × input rate):   USD 0.051422\r\n  Corrected    (Talon evidence, cache-aware):          USD 0.035334\r\n  Delta        (what naïve math would misreport):      USD 0.016089\r\n"]
[35.417534, "o", "\r\n  ✓ Corrected total is what the budget gate enforced against\r\n    → Recompute it yourself: rates in pricing/models.yaml × tokens in the export\r\n    → Export: out/session-evidence.json (signed records)\r\n\r\n"]
[35.434851, "o", "\r\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n[7/7] Session rollup + signature verification\r\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\n  The whole session — two providers, allowed work, both denials — is one\r\n  auditable unit. Every record's HMAC must verify."]
[35.435319, "o", "\r\n\r\n  talon audit list --session sess-governed-1783414113\r\n"]
[35.796712, "o", "  Session sess-governed-1783414113"]
[35.797232, "o", "\r\n"]
