[36.106999, "o", "─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\n  ✓ Real two-provider session  — Anthropic planner + OpenAI executors\r\n  ✓ Prompt-cache economics     — writes and reads priced exactly\r\n  ✓ Session budget gate        — cross-provider spend capped pre-forward\r\n  ✓ PII stop                   — IBAN never left the boundary\r\n  ✓ Tool governance            — admin_* stripped before the model\r\n  ✓ Signed evidence            — every record verified, 0 invalid\r\n\r\n  Talon provides enforceable controls and supporting evidence for your\r\n  GDPR / EU AI Act reviews; compliance remains your determination.\r\n\r\n"]
